# TaskFlow — Database

- Foreign keys with explicit `ON DELETE CASCADE` where children must disappear with parent.
- Index FK columns and frequent sort columns (`position`, `due_date`, etc.).
- Versioned SQL migrations under `database/migrations/`.
- PDO with prepared statements only; no string-interpolated SQL.
- Task `priority`: MySQL `ENUM('low','medium','high','urgent')` (or equivalent documented convention).
- UUIDs: `ramsey/uuid` or `bin2hex(random_bytes(16))` — stay consistent with existing migrations.
